body.name: L Shaped Computer Desk - 58" Gaming Desk, Reversible Corner Desk, Home Office Writing Desk with Monitor Stand Shelf, Space-Saving Modern Simple Wooden Desk, Rustic Brown
features: 【SPACIOUS WORKING AND STORAGE AREA】Dimension: 58"*39.4"*29.5". This home office desk maximally utilizes your home office space for corner space. The wide tabletop provides a comfortable space for study, writing, and the generous under-desk space is great for relaxing your legs.

【ONE DESK IN 2 STYLE】An L shaped computer desk or a large long desk, just choose one of style to assemble as you like. The corner desk is suitable for any corner place, and the long table style satisfys two people to work at the same time, when it be used as a home office desk.
【REVERSIBLE DESIGN】With reversible design, the L-shape desk is configured either on the right or left side as your personal preference.
【CABLE MANAGMENT】This computer desk has provide two cable management on the desktop to help store wires. That helps to make the desktop neat and tidy.

【2 MOVEABLE MONITOR STAND】This computer desk provides two removable monitor stands to help elevate the monitor and maintain a good sitting position. When stacking the two monitor stands, a two-tier small storage shelf would be get easily.

【STURDY AND SOLID CONSTRUCTION】Constructed by two high-quality MDF Boards and thicken Metal Frame, this L-shaped desk ensures stability and durability. With our detailed instructions, the installation process can be easy and fast.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Space-Saving Brilliance with a Reversible Corner Desk
reviews.reviewText: I recently upgraded my home office with this reversible corner desk, and it has truly transformed my workspace. The design is not only modern and sleek but also incredibly practical for maximizing the use of a corner.Assembly was straightforward, thanks to clear instructions, and the build quality is impressive. What sets this desk apart is its reversible feature, allowing flexibility in arranging the layout to suit different room configurations. This adaptability is a game-changer, making it a versatile option for various office setups.The desk offers a generous workspace, accommodating multiple monitors and providing ample room for other essentials. Cable management is well thought out, keeping the workspace tidy and organized.Sturdiness is a notable feature – the desk feels robust and stable even with the reversible design. The materials used are of high quality, and the finish adds a touch of elegance to the overall look.In conclusion, if you're in need of a space-saving, versatile, and stylish desk for your home office, this reversible corner desk is an excellent investment. It combines functionality with a modern aesthetic, creating an efficient and visually appealing workspace.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very good product. Every piece perfect.
reviews.reviewText: It's a great desk. Easy to put together as long as you pay attention to which way the parts go! I usually get it right but reversed two pieces and had to unscrew them and then screw them back together. If it wasn't easy to put together this would have been really hard! As it was it was a snap. Love the clean, smooth look. Every piece was perfect which was a testament to how well it was packaged. The outside box was so beat up I was sure the pieces were going to be damaged but not a single one was! Easy to put together and just great looking! Very satisfied with this desk and would order another if I had more room! Would make a great second work table!
